        - [Let's Take This Offline](http://diveintohtml5.org/offline.html)
        - [Appcache Facts](http://appcachefacts.info/)
        - [MDN: Offline resources in Firefox](http://developer.mozilla.org/En/Offline_resources_in_Firefox#The_cache_manifest)
